            </div>
            <div class="p-8 lg:p-12 order-1 lg:order-2">
              <div class="inline-block bg-crisp-orange/10 rounded-xl px-4 py-2 mb-4">
                <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-crisp-orange">🔗 Integration</span>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-crisp-green mb-4">API Development & Integration</h3>
